CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 27th November, 2004

The undersigned
directed to say that Shri Shibu Soren has been sworn in
as the Cabinet Minister by the President at 1500 hours today, the 27th November,
2004, in the Rashtrapati Bhavan, New Delhi.
Aum.
